{"tid":1594936,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國情報高官淪為中國間諜遭判10年","createTime":"2019-09-25T21:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T02:21:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d16713fcad5e576cd932fda74f83a800112e2445","tid":1594936,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T21:49:01.000Z","msg":"美國情報高官淪為中國間諜遭判10年<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190925-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E6%B7%AA%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E9%81%AD%E5%88%A410%E5%B9%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190925-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%25B7%25AA%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2588%25A410%25E5%25B9%25B4&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTso9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=cd8db501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190925-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E6%B7%AA%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E9%81%AD%E5%88%A410%E5%B9%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國60歲的韓森來自猶他州西勒鳩斯（Syracuse），因諜事暴露被捕，在今年3月認罪，坦承試圖將美國國防機密資訊泄露給中國，並收受數十萬美元擔任北京政府的特務。韓森獲取機密情報時，遭同事釣魚檢舉。韓森領刑10年。</strong><br />\n<br />\n據世界日報今天報道，向中國泄露國防機密，美前情報官遭判刑10年。該報道稱美國國防情報局前情報官韓森因為從事間諜活動並出售國防機密給中國，被聯邦法院判處10年徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n據美國司法部表示，國防情報局（Defense Intelligence Agency）前情報官韓森（Ron Rockwell Hansen）因為從事間諜活動並出售國防機密給中國，今天他被聯邦法院判處10年徒刑。報道引據路透社消息，60歲的韓森來自猶他州西勒鳩斯（Syracuse），他在今年3月認罪，坦承試圖將美國國防機密資訊泄露給中國，並收受數十萬美元擔任北京政府的幹員。<br />\n<br />\n據美國司法部表示，聯邦調查局（FBI）幹員在2018年6月逮捕韓森，當時他正前往西雅圖&ndash;塔科馬國際機場（Seattle-Tacoma International Airport）準備搭機飛往中國。<br />\n<br />\n該消息說，韓森認罪時坦承從一名國防情報局的專案官員那裡蒐集對中國有價值的美國國家安全資訊，並同意將相關資訊出售給中方。韓森從這名國防情報局官員收到的文件涉及美國軍事戰備狀況。但這名專案官員在韓森不知情的情況下向國防情報局舉報他的行徑，並擔任這起案件的聯邦調查局線人。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述聯邦法院文件指出，韓森操著一口流利的華語和俄語，曾在美國陸軍服役，並於2006年獲聘在國防情報局任職，承辦徵募及管理外國情報資產業務。報道指韓森也坦承中國情報人員在2014年招募他。"},{"pid":"ae6645488bde4cc8ef170c7d3be804710c50c939","tid":1594936,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda1685a74f2bd3ccd9b4bc7f4944eee6d69f11a","tid":1594936,"uid":68669,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:47:07.000Z","msg":"究竟邊個先會唔收錢都愛國呢"},{"pid":"116829a4830136e1664c58acdb295a2501e25bfe","tid":1594936,"uid":31200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:53:32.000Z","msg":"韓森<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e361593b72e11012686784710818dbfa41cb5f2","tid":1594936,"uid":130438,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:55:41.000Z","msg":"幾十萬就收買到..."},{"pid":"552e948ab83beee74dbe08c64b30290392373a01","tid":1594936,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81844fe30bc32d008cb659516d2683e936a1ad3b","tid":1594936,"uid":172627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fda1685a74f2bd3ccd9b4bc7f4944eee6d69f11a","tid":1594936,"uid":68669,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:47:07.000Z","msg":"究竟邊個先會唔收錢都愛國呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:14:13.000Z","msg":"Trump"},{"pid":"6b59f19fc34ba9822b385026842c9162d6b2d83f","tid":1594936,"uid":39698,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"116829a4830136e1664c58acdb295